  <dashboards>
    <dashboard name='Brand Positioning' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>&lt;Sheet Name&gt;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='223' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1416' minheight='964' minwidth='1416' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98870' x='565' y='830'>
            <zone h='3423' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98870' x='565' y='830' />
            <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98870' x='565' y='4253' />
            <zone h='84440' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98870' x='565' y='14730'>
              <flipboard active-id='4' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Brand Equity Strength: Awareness and Perception' captured-sheet='Brand Equity Positioning' id='1' />
                  <story-point caption='Usage Behavior Funnel: From Trial to Habitual Use' captured-sheet='Brand Funnel' id='2'>
                    <capturedDeltas>
                      <worksheet name='Brand Funnel'>
                        <filter class='categorical' column='[federated.0llut5508z5sp00zsic8y1aveno9].[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]'>
                          <groupfilter function='union' user:ui-domain='database' user:ui-enumeration='inclusive' user:ui-marker='enumerate'>
                            <groupfilter function='member' level='[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]' member='&quot;Daily&quot;' />
                            <groupfilter function='member' level='[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]' member='&quot;P1M&quot;' />
                            <groupfilter function='member' level='[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]' member='&quot;P3M&quot;' />
                            <groupfilter function='member' level='[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]' member='&quot;Trial&quot;' />
                            <groupfilter function='member' level='[none:Pivot Field Names:nk]' member='&quot;Weekly&quot;' />
                          </groupfilter>
                        </filter>
                      </worksheet>
                    </capturedDeltas>
                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='Perception–Behavior Gap Analysis' captured-sheet='Decomposition View' id='3' />
                  <story-point caption='Consumer Value Segment Performance Analysis' captured-sheet='Consumer Value Segment Performance Analysis' id='4' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='6846' hidden='true' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='36017' y='20021'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>The brand demonstrates strong equity performance across key perceptual dimensions, including awareness, spontaneous recall, and brand likability.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='8402' hidden='true' id='7' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='35876' y='34959'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>High awareness indicates strong market visibility, while elevated spontaneous awareness suggests strong mental availability within the category.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='6846' hidden='true' id='8' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='6992' y='64523'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>In contrast to strong brand equity, usage behavior reveals a clear decline as engagement frequency increases.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6846' hidden='true' id='9' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='36158' y='52075'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>Additionally, strong likability reflects positive emotional perception among consumers who are familiar with the brand.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6846' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='36299' y='68983'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>Overall, the brand maintains a strong perceptual position in the market, indicating that it is well-recognized and positively evaluated by consumers.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='22614' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='14760' x='70763' y='36722'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>While trial and recent usage (P3M and P1M) remain relatively strong, there is a noticeable drop in weekly usage, indicating challenges in converting initial engagement into habitual consumption.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6846' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='51201' y='65145'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>This pattern suggests that the brand successfully attracts users but faces limitations in sustaining long-term routine usage.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6120' hidden='true' id='13' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='54025' y='15871'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>A clear divergence exists between strong brand perception and declining usage intensity across behavioral stages.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6846' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='9534' y='36618'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>While the brand successfully achieves high awareness and strong likability, this strength does not fully translate into sustained frequent usage.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='9129' hidden='true' id='15' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='33333' x='51554' y='61411'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>The drop-off from trial and recent usage into weekly engagement indicates that consumers are willing to try and occasionally use the brand but are less likely to incorporate it into regular consumption routines.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='13278' hidden='true' id='16' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='16172' x='82980' y='79564'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>This disconnect highlights an important opportunity to improve usage retention and strengthen habitual engagement.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='12656' id='17' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='19774' x='79944' y='33091'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>The target brand demonstrates stronger advocacy performance within premium and super-premium consumer segments relative to the overall market.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='14938' id='18' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='19562' x='80155' y='51245'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>While usage penetration remains competitive across most funnel stages, the brand’s NPS advantage becomes increasingly visible among higher-spending consumers.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='14212' id='19' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='19562' x='80014' y='77801'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Baskerville'>This indicates that the brand resonates more strongly with premium-oriented customers, suggesting successful positioning within higher-value consumption tiers.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{3C4AB5C6-96AB-4CDD-8764-3C62EE7DAF70}' />
    </dashboard>
